Near China Grove / Mile Marker 68 to 63 Both Directions. Construction of four additional&nbsp;travel lanes (two in each direction) to approximately&nbsp;5 miles of I-85 from north of&nbsp;Lane Street&nbsp;(Exit 63) to north of&nbsp;NC152 (Exit 68) in&nbsp;Rowan County. Interchange improvements are also planned for interchanges at&nbsp;NC152 (MM 68) and Old Beatty Ford (MM 65).&nbsp; Bridges between Lane Street and NC 152 will also be replaced for I-85 expansion.&nbsp;This project will complete the expansion of I-85 through&nbsp;Rowan County providing a greater level of service for local and through traffic. The Contractor will need to have&nbsp;nightly lane&nbsp;closures along I-85&nbsp;for&nbsp;construction of the&nbsp;I-85 widening project&nbsp;. Closures can take place in the&nbsp;inside or in the outside lanes. Closures could be located on North Bound or South Bound of I-85.
